---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro'; import '../styles/marketing-pages.css';
---
<SiteLayout title="Contact Mault | Talk About AI Code Governance" description="Talk with Mault about deterministic governance for AI-written code, enterprise requirements, or a 45-day pilot." canonical="/contact/"><header class="mp-hero"><div class="shell"><p class="eyebrow">Contact</p><h1 class="display">Let’s talk about <span class="gradient-text">governed AI development.</span></h1><p class="lede">Tell us where coding agents are creating rework, review debt, or audit gaps. We’ll map the highest-value control point.</p></div></header><section class="section mp-band"><div class="shell mp-hero-grid"><div><p class="eyebrow">What happens next</p><h2 class="mp-section-title">A technical conversation, not a sales script.</h2><div class="mp-steps"><article class="mp-step"><h3>Understand your stack</h3><p>Agents, repositories, CI/CD, team size, and current governance controls.</p></article><article class="mp-step"><h3>Find the control gap</h3><p>Identify where attribution, enforcement, or evidence breaks down.</p></article><article class="mp-step"><h3>Define a useful pilot</h3><p>Scope one workflow with measurable outcomes and a clear evidence deliverable.</p></article></div><p><a href="mailto:contact@mault.ai" style="color:var(--green)">contact@mault.ai</a></p></div><form class="mp-form" data-demo-form><div class="mp-form-row"><label>First name<input name="firstName" required autocomplete="given-name"/></label><label>Last name<input name="lastName" required autocomplete="family-name"/></label></div><label>Work email<input name="email" type="email" required autocomplete="email"/></label><label>Company<input name="company" required autocomplete="organization"/></label><div class="mp-form-row"><label>Role<input name="role" autocomplete="organization-title"/></label><label>Team size<select name="teamSize"><option>2–10</option><option>11–50</option><option>51–200</option><option>200+</option></select></label></div><label>What are you looking to govern?<textarea name="message" rows="5" required></textarea></label><button class="button" type="submit">Request a conversation</button><p class="mp-form-status" data-form-status>This independent demo does not transmit submissions.</p></form></div></section><script>document.querySelector('[data-demo-form]')?.addEventListener('submit',(event)=>{event.preventDefault();const status=document.querySelector('[data-form-status]');if(status)status.textContent='Demo submission captured locally. No email or data was sent.'});</script></SiteLayout>
